{"tid":1487822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[[[大家入黎睇！！]]]8.25荃葵青遊行！！","createTime":"2019-08-19T12:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:42:24.000Z","uid":302813,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"74d96ee00454c6d00d0e3df37bfe890ec0cf81c4","tid":1487822,"uid":302813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"起點同時間都改左呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於申請康文署場地作遊行起點需要購買保險，而剛才接保險公司通知，遊行活動保險難以獲批，故起點將由原來之「葵涌運動場」改為「葵芳（南）巴士總站」為起點。同時，舉行集會及遊行時間亦將提前半小時。就多次改動引致手足們不便，我地謹此致歉。<br />\n故暫定有關825荃葵青遊行詳情如下 最終資料仍以獲發不反對通知書後所訂之內容為準：<br />\n<br />\n舉行日期：2019年8月25日<br />\n時間：1430（集會）1500（遊行隊伍出發）<br />\n起點：葵芳（南）巴士總站<br />\n終點：荃灣公園<br />\n<br />\n具體計劃之路線：<br />\n葵芳南總站-經行人隧道往葵福路（南行）天橋-橫跨興芳路-落行人天橋近葵福路（北行）-葵福路（北行）-葵福路與德士古道交界横過行人路處上行人天橋-橫過德士古道-落行人天橋近德士古道（北行）-楊屋道（西行）-入荃灣公園廣場<br />\n<br />\n聚焦目標：<br />\n1. 五大訴求（撤回逃犯條例修訂草案、撤銷所有義士控罪、徹查並追究所有黑警開槍血腥鎮壓之責任、撤回暴動定性、我要真&middot;雙普選）<br />\n2. 要求全面追究參與警黑合作、發動及參與721元朗及805荃灣恐怖襲擊之恐怖份子的所有刑事責任<br />\n3. 要求全面追究涉事插贓嫁禍、妨礙司法公正之警員責任<br />\n4. 抗議警察偽裝示威者，及其發動的一切暴力行為<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！不撤不散！<br />\n825約定大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635700a9acce99926ca38d2a5684965ae8ff7918","tid":1487822,"uid":228431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"係咪應該加d 訴求針對地區問題，如mtr放tg, 光頭佬舉槍"},{"pid":"3df48695089d919203b07461b70195e709794566","tid":1487822,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a01db699a5226ac968383e73114e3c5c6e59ee25","tid":1487822,"uid":20497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qebho8C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQebho8C.jpg&h=c00f8aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"17d349b0c617442adf70058bccf8d8a52f9ff7af","tid":1487822,"uid":302999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">TUI BAO KUI！！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14db832e25c5567a296d47940da0996161df6d6e","tid":1487822,"uid":302813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DtaaKao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDtaaKao.jpg&h=71c26818&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDnwtB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDnwtB3.jpg&h=e342400d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZtzroK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZtzroK.jpg&h=5045715c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vnTGW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vnTGW5.jpg&h=795c31cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11603aedd8304edfc76a8c29e606de33de595f3c","tid":1487822,"uid":302813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cf2b2d669b5f9f5a6f38f3fe30a507ca5587363","tid":1487822,"uid":96952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"ac58021e65aee344cdff559650989f3a2dcb0c05","tid":1487822,"uid":291987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"幫"},{"pid":"7a6ae82df402d9bac3a88a739325a63d70f2c10d","tid":1487822,"uid":291987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:42:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}